About us
Future Academic Research is an academic social networking website dedicated to providing
an environment inspiring the free exchange of brilliant academic ideas. We give researchers opportunities to
share research papers, carry out academic discussion and online peer view, or even produce teaching material
using their own research outcomes and launch to the public.
We believe Future Academic Research will accelerate the distribution of knowledge among
all intellectual individuals, thus inspiring equality, creativity and innovation.
Post Your Academic Research
View Research Feed
Open-Source Education Platform
On Future Academic Research, you can
post your academic research and include
information such as your contact details,
research topics, title and content. It
allows you to share your ideas with
the world, and we have made things
easier than arXiv.org and Google Scholar.
The users of our website, typically
researchers and students, can view
the posts by other people, making it
simple to get new ideas and understand
latest trends in the academic areas that
you are interested in. You can also set up
RSS on our website to receive
updates of new content.
We further implement the profiles of our users
which you can view. On those profiles, you will
find information such as their institutions,
positions, academic areas and contact details.
We encourage you to go from there and start
academic discussions with people that
have similar research interests.
